<body>
	<div class="markdown-body entry-content">
		<h1>This is WuShuYi Qrcode Dome</h1>
		<p>WuShuYi Qrcode is a python application</p>
		<h2>How To</h2>
		<p>
			The dome is
			<a href="./qrcode/">WuShuYi Qrcode</a>
		</p>
		<h5>Options:</h5>
		<ul>
			<li>
				url -- set qrcode content <br />
				example: <a href="./qrcode/?url=http://wushuyi.com/">http://localhost/qrcode/?url=http://wushuyi.com</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				dl -- set auto download on open default off [off]|[on]<br />
				example: <a href="./qrcode/?url=http://wushuyi.com/&dl=on">http://localhost/qrcode/?url=http://wushuyi.com&dl=on</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				size -- set qrcode size (size in 0~100)<br />
				example: <a href="./qrcode/?size=20">http://localhost/qrcode/?size=20</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				border -- set qrcode border (border in 0~100)<br />
				example: <a href="./qrcode/?border=10">http://localhost/qrcode/?border=10</a>
			</li>
		</ul>
